description:
It’s all about strong female vibes this week as Anna and Sim welcome the beautiful, brilliant Sophia Bush (One Tree Hill, Chicago PD) to chat about...

  • College fashion and the Greek scene
  • Self-confidence and self-acceptance
  • Acting, stunt-work, and kissing on-screen
  • Dating Deal-Breakers and some ski-trip improv

On the phones this week...

  • Courtney, 27, is calling from Seattle where she has a job and a boyfriend that she loves – but after finding out about her boyfriend out of state job offer, she needs help deciding what to put first – her career or her relationship.

 

Follow us!

Anna Faris: @annakfaris

Unqualified: @unqualified

Sophia Bush: @SophiaBush
